latestPosts.caption:
Stumbled upon something unexpectedly beautiful yesterday— a group art show by Lito Apostolakou titled “Clothes You Will Never Wear.”
Each piece had its own story, a unique perspective, a quiet little truth stitched into fabric.
Funny how sometimes the most meaningful things are the ones you don’t plan — they just find you. 🎨👗
